entries.femaleVariant: Will ya sit with me a while?
[Sit] Mornin'.
So... yesterday... What was that, exactly?
The beginning of something amazing.
A pleasant distraction.
Think it was the same for you and me both...
entries.maleVariant: I think it was the same for you and me both...

entries.femaleVariant: Think it... I mean... I hope it was the beginning of something nice.
entries.maleVariant: I think it... I mean, I hope it was the beginning of somethin' nice.

entries.femaleVariant: Meanin'?
Releasing tension. Right. 'Course.
Unless... you see things differently?
entries.maleVariant: Unless you see things, uh... differently?

entries.femaleVariant: Y'know... yesterday, I think I'd made up my mind...
Actually called you 'cause I wanted to say goodbye.
What're you trying to say?!
Night City's not for everyone.
Since I've known you, Judy, all you've been is chaotic, unstable and hotheaded.
Gimme your hand, V.
[Give hand]
What for?
Why? What for?
I don't know what to say...
You sure?
It's like that joke…
Dunno what to say... Nobody's ever done anything like this for me. Really shows trust.
Don't say anything. Just gimme your hand.
All set, congrats. Just gave you unlimited access to my pad.
I-if it's what you want. Or just drop by when the urge grabs you.
You sure? Isn't exactly a small thing, this...
entries.maleVariant: You sure about this? Haven't known each other that long.

entries.femaleVariant: It's like that joke... Know the one?
entries.maleVariant: It's like that joke, uh... Y'know the one?

entries.femaleVariant: Wanna go there now?
Look, Night City's not for everyone. Grew up here, thought nothin' could surprise me...
entries.maleVariant: Look, Night City's not for everyone. I grew up here, thought nothin' could surprise me...

entries.femaleVariant: It'll be the same anywhere else.
People shouldn't live so cramped together, on top of each other.
Y'know... think if you lined up all cities next to each other, they'd look the same.
Know why I came to Night City? 'Cause I thought it offered opportunities you couldn't come by anywhere else.
And now?
Maybe so... Maybe all cities got allurin' faces... But stay long in one and you see what's behind it.
I feel you...
Don't remember, or you want me to remind you?
entries.maleVariant: You don't remember? Or do you want me to remind you?

entries.femaleVariant: You know exactly what I'm tryna say. What did it mean, like, to you?
Pleasant distraction. A chance to let loose, nice way to spend the evening...
I'd better get goin'.
Ugh... Can be such a gonk sometimes.
City's chewed me up, an' it's spittin' me out.
M'gonna miss you too, V...
I'd pack up my shit and bail too, if I could…
But... it's just not the right time.
Corps're makin' sure of that. Makin' life uniform, everywhere.
entries.maleVariant: Corps're makin' sure of that, makin' life uniform. Everywhere.

entries.femaleVariant: I... I can't leave Night City yet.
Now it feels like I'm standin' in quicksand. That's no way to live... for anyone.
entries.maleVariant: Now, it feels like I'm standin' in quicksand. That's no way to live... for anyone.

entries.femaleVariant: I... I can't leave Night City, not yet. But someday – who knows.
You can if you want. Gonna stick around for a bit before I head back.
I like you. Wanna see you lots. Way I see it, there isn't anything else to consider.
Ummm, no...?
"What do lesbians bring on their second date?" Moving vans. Both.
Ah-- Oh, that one? Vintage as groaners go.
Wait.
H-hang on... that-- that didn't come out quite right.
entries.maleVariant: Hang on... that didn't come out quite right.

entries.femaleVariant: See ya.
See ya, Judy.
entries.maleVariant: I'll see ya, Judy.

entries.femaleVariant: Yeah, bye, V. Have a nice life.
Meant what you said, V. Don't pretend like you can take it back.
Let's not make this longer than it needs to be. See ya, V.
Judy... s-sorry. Thought you felt the same way.
entries.maleVariant: Judy... sorry, I... I thought you felt the same way.

entries.femaleVariant: You thought one thing, I thought another. Crossed wires, it happens.
Whoa, hah... Askin' me to move in?
entries.maleVariant: Whoa... Askin' me to move in?

entries.femaleVariant: Mornin'.
Sure about this? Haven't known each other that long...
I like you, consider you a friend. Way I see it, there's nothing else to consider.
Take care, V.
This really it? Last time we see each other? Didn't seem so set on leaving just a sec ago.
See no reason to delay. I'll stay here a couple days... then head off.
It's been nice knowin' ya, V.
See ya... And hit me up on the holo sometimes.
[Stand]
[Stand] Later.
See ya, Judy.
entries.maleVariant: I'll see ya, Judy.

entries.femaleVariant: Here's your coffee. Finally.
You're crazy. But I'll miss ya.
Gonna miss ya.
entries.maleVariant: I'm gonna miss ya.

entries.femaleVariant: Ruined my plans, you know that?
Was gonna leave Night City in the dust, for good. Even started packing.
Why did you wanna leave?
Why'd you wanna leave?
Oh, well, guess I'll have to make it up to you, won't I?
entries.maleVariant: Oh, well, uh... I guess I'll have to make it up to ya, won't I?

entries.femaleVariant: Positively burst into my life, you did, so I should've expected an ending just as abrupt, like this...
entries.maleVariant: Positively burst into my life, you did... so I should've expected an ending just as abrupt, like this...

entries.femaleVariant: Gonna make it up to you, somehow.
But now I think... Think I gotta stay.
Y'know, everything that happened... Guess it just got to me.
But now, from where I stand... Night City's started to feel like the place to be.
Hm... Yeah, that would be appropriate.
The fuck, Judy? Sayin' you wanna leave? Now?
entries.maleVariant: The fuck, Judy? You sayin' you wanna leave? Now?

entries.femaleVariant: Y'know, had this bizarre convo with a doll... Told me I had to fight. And I thought – fight for what?
entries.maleVariant: Y'know, I had this bizarre convo with a doll... Told me I had to fight. And I thought – fight for what?

entries.femaleVariant: It's not like we won't keep in touch...
And now, just when I thought I knew what it was all for... Friendship, trust... You're tellin' me you're leavin'?
entries.maleVariant: And now, just when I thought I knew what it was all for... Friendship, trust... You're tellin' me you're leavin'.

entries.femaleVariant: [Pick up clothes]
[Pick up clothes]
[Drink]
